                     <interp inst="t18300415-198-person1767" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I overtook the prisoner with the pork about two hundred yards from the shop; he was carrying it in his smock frock - he said he had bought it at Whitechapel.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300415-198-person1768">
                  HANNAH 
                  HOLT
               <interp inst="t18300415-198-person1768" type="surname" value="HOLT"></interp>
