                     <interp inst="t18300415-198-person1768" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw the prisoner go out of the shop backwards - I suspected he had done something wrong, and I said to my uncle he has taken something; he was brought back afterwards.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300415-198-person1769">
                  THOMAS 
                  BURFORD
               <interp inst="t18300415-198-person1769" type="surname" value="BURFORD"></interp>
