                     <interp inst="t18300415-198-person1769" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I took the prisoner, and found this stick with a hook at the end of it, and the pork was lacerated with the hook.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I met a man who asked me to have a bit of meat which he showed me - I said I had not money for it; he wanted 7s. - I was going away, but was called back and had it for 6s.</p>
               <p>
